  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate if the developed theory and evidence based programme
      has a positive effect on mother's breastfeeding self efficacy, establishing an effective
      breastfeeding and breastfeeding duration after short time hospitalization.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
